lead_paragraph: GlenFed Inc., owner of Glendale Federal Bank in Glendale, Calif., the nation's fifth-largest savings and loan association, is fighting for its life. Confronted by a California economy on the ropes and Federal regulators embarrassed by their failure to prevent widespread collapses in the savings industry, GlenFed is battling on two fronts.

headline.main: Dual Effort To Survive By GlenFed
